 less than 1\u00a0hr using a desktop computer with sufficient resolution to detect increases in arousals during midwinter in both species and clear signals of daily arousal periodicity in infected\n                    M. sodalis\n                    .\n                  \n                \n                \n                  \n                    Our unexpected finding of periodic synchronous group arousals in hibernating bats demonstrate the potential for video methods and suggest some bats may have innate behavioural strategies for coping with\n                    WNS\n                    . Surveillance video and accessible analysis software make it now practical to investigate long\u2010term behaviours of hibernating bats and other hard\u2010to\u2010study animals.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Hayman, David T. S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Cryan, Paul M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fricker, Paul D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dannemiller, Nicholas G.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Freckleton, Robert", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/0d0290c424bbaaa1dc5e107328ec9141", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/0dd88eea487e4ea475e85478c4b3ed324979c059f931753a4bdb2266faf9fe97", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/MSDF56K8", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/MSDF56K8", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/9bbdae9c21cf6851569a8f191b97c327!/b132177-134741", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy"